query_last_opponent

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_last_opponent -  This method returns the last known opponent we attacked or defended against.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
object query_last_opponent()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
object the opponent.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/combat.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the last known opponent we attacked or defended
against.  It is kept as up to date as the system can manage and so will
include anyone who is currently attacking us or who we are currently
attacking.

.EP

